.jumbotron
  %center
    %h1 Welcome to EngineeringFinder!
    %h4 View, share, comment and find team for thesis realization!
    - if user_signed_in?
      = link_to "Join us!", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary"


- unless categories.present?
  %h2
    %center
      We're sorry, there are no categories added (yet)!!!
- else
  - categories.each do |category|
    .row
      .col-md-8
        = category.name
      .col-md-2
        Theses in this category:
        = category.thesis.count
      .col-md-2
        = link_to "Show", category_path(category), class: "btn btn-info"
